    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this absolute beauty. It's in such incredible shape, it honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've babied this car from day one, and it shows\u2014not a scratch or dent in sight! It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
