    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been garage-kept, pampered, and meticulously cared for. You won\u2019t find a single blemish on it. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
