      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This specimen is mechanically superlative, boasting a comprehensive double-VANOS service and documented valve clearance adjustments. The chassis integrity is guaranteed via preventative rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring the factory-spec torsional rigidity remains uncompromised. Power is managed through a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a tight limited-slip differential. The vehicle retains its original suspension geometry and exhibits zero fluid seepage or bushing deflection. This is an investment-grade example with flawless paint depth and a preserved interior, delivering the precise tactile feedback and linear throttle response these M-cars are world-renowned for.",
